00:01:17.960 --> 00:01:20.400
covering everything from
basic arithmetic all

00:01:20.400 --> 00:01:22.720
the way to vector calculus
and some of the stuff

00:01:22.720 --> 00:01:24.490
that you saw up there.

00:01:24.490 --> 00:01:27.820
We have a million students
